text: Francesco Mussoni (born 15 May 1971) is a Captain Regent of San Marino from 1 October 2009 to 1 April 2010 and a second time together with Giacomo Simoncini from 1 October 2021 to 1 April 2022. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Captains Regent of San Marino Category:Living people Category:Current national leaders
title: Francesco Mussoni
